item.title: Hanna – Lost My Head (Потеряла голову)
item.description: Ханна is Anna Vladimirovna Ivanova (1991), from Cheboksary. More on Genius.com and Wikipedia (RU). Also on VK and this website. Video with and without intro. In this PROКлип, Ханна talks about making the video (МУЗ-ТВ, 2016, 3 m). Released in 2015, written by Kirbaba Pavel.
